Billy Milton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Billy_Milton 0 Billy Milton (1905–1989) was a British stage, film and television actor. Born in Paddington, Middlesex, as William Thomas Milton, he was the son of Harry Harman Milton (1880-1942), a commission agent, and his wife Hilda Eugenie Milton, née Jackson, (1878-1935).
